) in ROOT\nhistogram fitting and corresponding performance gains from offloading to GPUs.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 11 Mar 2022 18:10:53 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 16 May 2022 16:53:14 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-03-01"}
