 join these studies and call for support of the R&D program\naimed at comprehensive demonstration of this approach that includes design,\nconstruction, and power tests of a long prototype of the HTS-based fast-cycling\naccelerator magnet by 2028.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 11 Mar 2022 21:05:39 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-03-15"}
